This is the delta function
shifted to c.

00:05:27.800 --> 00:05:30.950
If I multiply that times
that, what do I get?

00:05:30.950 --> 00:05:34.060
This is kind of the key
intuition here.

00:05:34.060 --> 00:05:37.410
Let me redraw my axes.

00:05:37.410 --> 00:05:41.500
Let me see if I can do it
a little bit straighter.

