00:05:44.930 --> 00:05:46.260
So that's t.

00:05:46.260 --> 00:05:48.480
So what happens when I
multiply these two?

00:05:48.480 --> 00:05:52.480
Everywhere, when t equals
anything other than c, the

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:55.570
Dirac delta function is zero.

00:05:55.570 --> 00:05:57.290
So it's zero times anything.

00:05:57.290 --> 00:05:58.560
I don't care what this function
