00:06:07.050 --> 00:06:10.110
At t equals c, what's the
value of the function?

00:06:10.110 --> 00:06:12.000
Well, it's going to
be the value of

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:14.070
the Dirac delta function.

00:06:14.070 --> 00:06:17.760
It's going to be the Dirac delta
function times whatever

00:06:17.760 --> 00:06:20.030
height this is.

00:06:20.030 --> 00:06:23.410
This is going to be this point
right here or this right

00:06:23.410 --> 00:06:26.530
