This is going to be e to the
minus sc times f of c.

00:06:39.765 --> 00:06:42.970
All I'm doing is I'm just
evaluating this function at c,

00:06:42.970 --> 00:06:45.150
so that's the point
right there.

00:06:45.150 --> 00:06:48.180
So if you take this point, which
is just some number, it

00:06:48.180 --> 00:06:51.840
could be 5, 5 times this, you're
