00:06:51.840 --> 00:06:53.140
the Dirac delta function.

00:06:53.140 --> 00:06:54.540
Or in this case, it's not 5.

00:06:54.540 --> 00:06:55.930
It's this little more
abstract thing.

00:06:55.930 --> 00:06:58.660
I could just draw
