00:08:13.500 --> 00:08:15.220
I said from zero to infinity.

00:08:15.220 --> 00:08:19.850
So if we take from zero to
infinity, what I'm saying is

00:08:19.850 --> 00:08:21.390
taking this integral
is equivalent

00:08:21.390 --> 00:08:23.160
to taking this integral.

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:31.260
So e to the minus sc f of c
times my delta function t

00:08:31.260 --> 00:08:34.270
minus c dt.

00:08:34.270 --> 00:08:37.179
Now, this thing right here, let
me make this very clear,

00:08:37.179 --> 00:08:41.280
I'm claiming that this is
equivalent to this.

00:08:41.280 --> 00:08:44.530
Because everywhere else, the
delta function zeroes out this

00:08:44.530 --> 00:08:47.300
function, so we only care about
this function, or e to

00:08:47.300 --> 00:08:50.430
the minus st f of t when
t is equal to c.

00:08:50.430 --> 00:08:52.810
And so that's why we were able
to turn it into a constant.

00:08:52.810 --> 00:08:54.920
But since this is a constant,
we can bring it out of the

00:08:54.920 --> 00:08:59.380
integral, and so this is equal
to-- I'm going to go backwards

00:08:59.380 --> 00:09:01.860
here just to kind of save space
and still give you these

00:09:01.860 --> 00:09:03.120
things to look at.

00:09:03.120 --> 00:09:07.690
If we take out the constants
from inside of the integral,

00:09:07.690 --> 00:09:14.540
we get e to the minus sc times f
of c times the integral from

00:09:14.540 --> 00:09:21.650
0 to infinity of f
of t minus c dt.

00:09:21.650 --> 00:09:23.830
Oh sorry, not f of t minus c.

00:09:27.520 --> 00:09:28.370
This is not an f.

00:09:28.370 --> 00:09:29.380
I have to be very careful.

00:09:29.380 --> 00:09:31.000
This is a delta.

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:33.160
Let me do that in a
different color.

00:09:33.160 --> 00:09:35.960
I took out the constant terms
there, and it's going to be a

00:09:35.960 --> 00:09:39.710
delta of t minus c dt.

00:09:42.410 --> 00:09:43.760
Let me get the right color.

00:09:46.350 --> 00:09:49.300
Now, what is this thing
by definition?

00:09:49.300 --> 00:09:50.370
This thing is 1.

00:09:50.370 --> 00:09:52.420
I mean, we could put it from
minus infinity to infinity, it

00:09:52.420 --> 00:09:53.150
