00:09:53.150 --> 00:09:55.170
The only time where it has any
area is right under c.

00:09:55.170 --> 00:09:57.110
So this thing is equal to 1.

00:09:57.110 --> 00:10:01.390
So this whole integral right
there has been reduced to this

00:10:01.390 --> 00:10:04.040
